title: Search Party with Brandon Jordan
overview: Search Party with Brandon Jordan follows Brandon Jordan across the country searching for items lost underwater in hopes to return them to their owners. Brandon and his crew polling their social media followers to crowdsource leads for locating lost items believed to be hiding below the surface. Brandon dives into oceans, lakes, rivers, and canals where he is challenged by weather, wildlife, and water conditions in his expedition to find items that were once someone's prized possession.
